title: BRIEF-FILAE H1 net result turns to profit of 0.2 million euros
text:
BRIEF-FILAE H1 net result turns to profit of 0.2 million euros 
Oct 14 FILAE : 
* Reports H1 net income of 0.2 million euros ($228,780) compared to loss of 0.3 million euros a year ago 
* H1 operating loss is 0.5 million euros compard to loss of 0.2 million euros a year ago 
* Q3 revenue is 1.3 million euros compared to 1.6 million euros a year ago Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8742 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
